<para>Allocates a <ref refid="structcorr__state__t" kindref="compound">corr_state_t</ref>, a dp_f32_t ring buffer of capacity next_pow2(max(n, 512)), and all scratch buffers. The ring buffer satisfies the dp_f32_create() page-alignment constraint automatically.</para>
